snippet: Shanshan Feng of China shot a nine-under-par 64 Saturday to take a one-stroke lead over Stacy Lewis after the third round of the Reignwood L.P.G.A. Classic in Beijing.
abstract: Shanshan Feng of China takes third-round lead at Reignwood LPGA Classic in Beijing; start of play was delayed because of the high levels of smog.
lead_paragraph: Shanshan Feng of China shot a nine-under-par 64 Saturday to take a one-stroke lead over Stacy Lewis after the third round of the Reignwood L.P.G.A. Classic in Beijing.
